{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01HSDqJEy26RYF4MoWqRNHLQ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The ConfigMap is correct. The issue is that the pod is still in CrashLoopBackOff from the old config. The pod restart via `kubectl rollout restart` should eventually pick up the new config, but the pod is in backoff mode. \n\nThe pod creates a new container each time it crashes. The configmap is mounted as a volume - but with `subPath`, the volume doesn't auto-update! That's the issue. When you use `subPath` to mount a ConfigMap, the file is NOT automatically updated when the ConfigMap changes. The pod needs to be recreated.\n\nHowever, since the rollout restart triggered a pod spec update (annotations change), when the pod next starts, it should use the new pod spec template. But the pod is in CrashLoopBackOff so it might not start with the new template.\n \nWith `rollout restart`, a new pod spec gets applied and the StatefulSet will terminate and recreate the pod with the updated template. I should force delete the pod to break it out of the backoff loop and let it restart with the new configuration.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1001,"cache_read_input_tokens":43319,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1001},"output_tokens":33,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"fd259128-069b-45cd-b525-e5e3bdceb713","uuid":"576c27c6-5086-49bb-af8a-078eb0efbd0f","request_id":"req_011CcQ96FMZyJBD1CcNFh4Ky"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01HSDqJEy26RYF4MoWqRNHLQ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"ConfigMap is correct. The pod needs a hard restart since `subPath` mounts don't auto-update. Force-delete the pod."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1001,"cache_read_input_tokens":43319,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1001},"output_tokens":33,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"fd259128-069b-45cd-b525-e5e3bdceb713","uuid":"97cb3a04-9a0f-4313-b0b9-9238cc8ec716","request_id":"req_011CcQ96FMZyJBD1CcNFh4Ky"}
