{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01HBaxDV1bm4eSNk5k8zUEVQ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The nodes are trying to discover each other but es-1 and es-2 don't exist yet because they weren't scheduled in the StatefulSet (the rollout deleted es-0 and it's recreating es-0 first, then will do es-1, es-2). The cluster is waiting for quorum (needs at least 2 nodes).\n\nThe issue is that only es-0 is running (the others haven't been created yet since we deleted them). With `cluster.initial_master_nodes` having 3 nodes, ES might need quorum to elect a master. With only 1 node running and 2 others not yet started, ES can't form a quorum.\nThis creates a deadlock: es-0 can't become Ready because it's waiting for the cluster to form with es-1 and es-2, but those pods won't be created until es-0 is Ready. It's a classic StatefulSet bootstrap problem where the first pod is stuck waiting for peers that haven't been scheduled yet.\n\nThe solution is to either enable parallel pod creation with `podManagementPolicy: Parallel` so all three pods start simultaneously, or temporarily configure just es-0 as the initial master node to let it bootstrap independently, then scale up afterward.\n\nSince I can't modify the pod management policy on an existing StatefulSet, I'll need to delete it and recreate it with the parallel policy enabled.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1090,"cache_read_input_tokens":48211,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1090},"output_tokens":30,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"fd259128-069b-45cd-b525-e5e3bdceb713","uuid":"360a066e-1143-45e7-99bd-1345c73539f3","request_id":"req_011CcQ9tZhfDphrUye7D6YR5"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01HBaxDV1bm4eSNk5k8zUEVQ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"es-0 is stuck waiting for es-1/es-2 (quorum), but StatefulSet `OrderedReady` won't create them until es-0 is Ready — a deadlock. I need to recreate the StatefulSet with `podManagementPolicy: Parallel`."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1090,"cache_read_input_tokens":48211,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1090},"output_tokens":30,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"fd259128-069b-45cd-b525-e5e3bdceb713","uuid":"aa6d6326-7336-4133-b057-a6fc12fd8182","request_id":"req_011CcQ9tZhfDphrUye7D6YR5"}
